      "range": "632-664",
      "markText": "行走是向内的勘察，而我们穿行其间的风景，又如何微妙地塑造着我们。",
      "totalCount": 406,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=632&rangeEnd=664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_7_1483-1504",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1483-1504",
      "markText": "雪让万物都超出自身，月光又使一切成双成对。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1483&rangeEnd=1504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1483&rangeEnd=1504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_3_409-422",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "409-422",
      "markText": "还有那些让小路始终畅通的人",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=409&rangeEnd=422",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=409&rangeEnd=422"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_7_591-611",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "591-611",
      "markText": "离冬至还有两天，一年的潮头至此又将折返。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=591&rangeEnd=611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_5_382-447",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "382-447",
      "markText": "这本书，静静坐着是写不出来的。它的主题是道路、行走和想象之间的关联，因此大量思考完成于徒步行走之际，也只有行走时才可能做这样的思考",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=382&rangeEnd=447",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=382&rangeEnd=447"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_8_6363-6424",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6363-6424",
      "markText": "博罗的性情冲动多变，和许多长途步行者一样，他有抑郁症，很小就被一种他称作“恐怖”的东西纠缠。走路成为他克服悲伤的一种方式。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6363&rangeEnd=6424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6363&rangeEnd=6424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_7_1149-1175",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1149-1175",
      "markText": "寒气吸入鼻中有如钢丝。满天繁星，银色的月光漫过万物。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1149&rangeEnd=1175",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1149&rangeEnd=1175"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_5_503-546",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "503-546",
      "markText": "笔者沿古道走了一千多英里，试图寻找一条通向往昔的路径，却一次又一次发现自己被送回当下。",
      "totalCount": 143,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=503&rangeEnd=546",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=503&rangeEnd=546"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_10_5061-5139",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5061-5139",
      "markText": "出发前两天，我的阿拉斯加朋友詹姆斯热心地建议我带上一把锋利的小斧子：“这样的话，如果你陷到泥潭里，潮水又涨上来了，你就能在脚踝那里下刀，把脚砍断，好逃命。”",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300100497&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5061&rangeEnd=5139",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ba1320d0813ab8dc1g01740b?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5061&rangeEnd=5139"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300100497_8_3537-3604",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3537-3604",
      "markText": "我还在记忆中走过成千上万里，因为每逢失眠——多数夜晚我都失眠——我便派出思绪，让它们重走我经过的小路，这样一来，有时走着走着便睡着了。",
